{"tid":1927124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外商急逃 星巴克反向投資中國1.3億美元 李克強發文謝謝","createTime":"2020-03-15T14:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:41:29.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea83bc5592ef746c6ad3c7ec07473ee8d09e744e","tid":1927124,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國爆發武漢肺炎疫情，惹得外企急逃，在此同時，美國星巴克咖啡反向操作，投資1.3億美元（約39億台幣）在中國江蘇崑山設立一座烘焙基地，這是星巴克在美國以外的最大筆單項生產投資，引得中國國務院總理李克強急忙發文表感謝。<br />\n<br />\n《澎湃新聞》報導，星巴克咖啡總部位於美國西雅圖，進入中國約20年，擁有逾4000家門市，去年在中國營收約30億美元（約900億台幣），佔全球營收265.09億美元（約7952.7億台幣）的11%，已在本月13日完成簽約，將在崑山設立一座咖啡烘培工廠，預計今年下半年動工、2022年夏天投產。<br />\n<br />\n在外商大舉逃出中國之際，星巴克逆向投資中國，李克強特別發信，感謝星巴克的投資，並指中國將會進一步放寬市場准入，且經濟長期看好，將繼續成為外資投資熱土。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，崑山距離上海市約51公里，位在長三角經濟圈內，但重點是，週邊是工業區，沒有咖啡產業，且整個中國都沒有成熟的咖啡文化，星巴克將烘培基地設在該處，連當地媒體都懷疑其風險過大。<br />\n<br />\n但蘇州崑山經濟技術開發區黨工委委員、管委會副主任潘建康則稱，平均中國每人一年喝8杯咖；相比之下，歐美人喝400杯，顯示市場潛力巨大。<br />\n<br />\n另據美媒報導，受到武漢肺炎疫情影響，星巴克中國門市Q2銷售額將減少50%，至4億到4.3億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3100261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100261&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=12626a7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100261&h=d3ef41ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3100261</a>"},{"pid":"857b86c4cd80a06f1e6871f864db814ae5b341b9","tid":1927124,"uid":318339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"Goodbye Starbucks!!!"},{"pid":"97a1dc8ce08d136642562196d84ab05ebc69d48e","tid":1927124,"uid":8810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:49:12.000Z","msg":"可以繼續罷飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a970eb5558f9a56638c6c6f8aa2050f256ab3c7b","tid":1927124,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />blacklst<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2677da6954c1674f6523c70f135d1814e7e69f76","tid":1927124,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"私下關幾多間分店唔提"},{"pid":"06d7efdcfcf41b647e2416f4091f661933383320","tid":1927124,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"已經放棄咗香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec374c5ac90d51ab96d8192b9de7f469c15d49c","tid":1927124,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=37d6ed00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fv0gy0cic5bzonwl%2Fstatus%2F1239189294700363777%3Fs%3D21&h=19bc6c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/v0gy0cic5bzonwl/status/1239189294700363777?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n［突發］有人整左維尼病毒公仔出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926864\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926864</a></blockquote>"}]}